# Public Google OAuth Client ID used by Google Identity Services for sign-in.
# It is public by design (sent to the browser) — but the OAuth *client secret*
# is NEVER used by this app, so do not put any secret here.
#
# Create one at: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# Add your site origin (e.g. https://your-app.pages.dev) to the client's
# "Authorized JavaScript origins".
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-google-oauth-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
